After examining several possible functions for goodness of fit, the rational equation, Eq. (2), was used to describe the relationship between leaf area index (LAI) and days after emergence. The function describing LAI, Eq. (2), was integrated from i days after emergence (ti) to j days after emergence (tj) to generate an estimate of leaf area duration (LADi−j) (Eq. 3). The mean net assimilation rate from ti to tj (mNARi−j) was calculated as the quotient of DMAi−j and LADi−j (Eq. 4) (Andrewh, Matt & Robertp, 2009). (2)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
